nan hendthi chennagidale ( kannada : ನನ ಹೆಂಡ ತಿ ಚೆನ ನಾಗಿದ ದಾಳೆ ) is a 2000 indian comedy film in kannada language starring kashi , anjani takkar and ananth nag in the lead roles along with vishnuvardhan , and ramesh aravind in special appearances .   the film is directed and written by dinesh babu .